    sage: pi = x^3-x^2-x-1 # Tribonacci
    sage: b = pi.roots(ring=QQbar)[1][0]
    sage: a = DetAutomaton(
    sage: m = BetaAdicSet(b, {0,1})
    sage: print(m)
    Monoid of b-adic expansion with b root of x^3 - x^2 - x - 1 and numerals set {0, 1}
    sage: pp = m.b.parent().places()[0]
